  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located just steps away from the Old Town, Ljubljana Castle and the main city attractions, the hotel has a modern and luxurious feel. Slovenia's characterful capital <a data-udi="umb://document/5cfd5f91c1d0419185792bc414ff7721" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5cfd5f91c1d0419185792bc414ff7721}" title="Ljubljana">Ljublijana</a> is on your doorstep. With a history that dates back hundreds of years, the iconic Hotel Slon has been frequently renovated to ensure it continues to offer high standards.</p>
<p>Visit the modern lounge and reception as well as the fitness centre and spa facilities, which include relaxing saunas with tropical rain showers. Restaurant Slon has views over the city street and has great cuisine. The restaurant uses Slovene and Mediterranean influences paired with a top wine selection.</p>
<p>Rooms are designed with a rich décor and attractive furnishings.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1hr hour by coach from Ljubljana airport and approx. 3hr-4hr hour by coach from Salzburg airport <span>with 30min stop on the way</span>.</p>]]></description>
